{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudstabbar"]}],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute","text":"MainActor"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSTabBar"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"genericParameter","text":"Content"},{"kind":"text","text":"> "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"where"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Content"},{"kind":"text","text":" : "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI4ViewP","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"View"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Navigations"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Appearances","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Appearances"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"iOS 26 brings Liquid Glass, the new Apple look and feel which will prevent developers to define specific styles for some critical components like bars."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Because today the OUDS tab bar relies on native component and is not designed from scratch, some elements will look different between iOS 26 and older versions:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"background color of tab bar can be changed for iOS lower than 26"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"background color of tab bar does not change since iOS 26"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"normal \/ unselected tab item color can be changed for both image and text only for iOS lower than 26"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"with iOS 26 no token of color are applied on unselected \/ normal tab item because only the image will be changed"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and not the text making theme not readable in dark color scheme"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In addition the badges colors will be the same and cannot be changed (except with token definition). These particular badges do not rely on "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBadge","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" componetabCountnt,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the native API is used instead."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Because Liquid Glass is available since iOS 26, the tab bar will be liquified \/ glassified since this OS version, not before."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you use SF Symbols for images, if they exist their "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"fill"}]},{"type":"text","text":" variant will be automatically used in the tab bar (native behaviour)."}]},{"text":"Platform considerations","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Platform-considerations"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This component is tailored for iOS"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"On iPadOS the tabs do not apply the fonts since iPadOS 18"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Because macOS does not support UIKit and because UIKIt is used to define the style of the tab bar, there is not styling of the tab bar for macOS"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"visionOS with is specific UI does not apply colors on tab bars and things are glasssified"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The component is not available for watchOS"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The component is not available for tvOS"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Guidelines","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Guidelines"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDS guidelines recommends to:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"limit when possible the number of items to 5"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"use both images and texts in tab bar items"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"use badges only when needed to avoid to have heavy tab bar"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"be sure the selected information is not only defined by the color of the tab; you may need to change the shape or the fill of the image"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"if a badge must be displayed, prefer short texts. If the text is a decimal value greater than 99, prefer display “+99”"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"if decorative images are used for tab bar item, apply "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"template","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" rendering mode on it to apply color on tabs"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Accessibility considerations","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If your tabs embedded in the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTabBar"},{"type":"text","text":" do not contain texts but only images, add an accessibility label introducing the journey for this tab"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If your tabs embedded in the "},{"code":"OUDSTabBar","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" display a badge (empty or with text), vocalize it in your tab to let users know what it is (unread messages, new things, etc)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"by using accessibiltiy value"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    OUDSTabBar {","        SomeView()","            .tabItem {","                Label {","                    Text(\"Emails\") \/\/ The text is vocalized first","                        .accessibilityValue(\"5 unread emails\") \/\/ A value vocalized after the text","            } icon: {","                Image(systemName: \"mail\").accessibilityHidden(true)","            }","        }","        .badge(5) \/\/ The value you give to the badge","    }",""]},{"text":"Selection of tabs","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Selection-of-tabs"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For iOS lower than 26, a selected tab indicator can be displayed in the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTabBar"},{"type":"text","text":" if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"count"},{"type":"text","text":" parameter is defined (to the number of tabs in the component)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"selectedTab"},{"type":"text","text":" binding value is equal to a given tag associated to a tab item."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Otherwise the indicator won’t appear; these parameters are mandatory to compute the location of the indicator."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This rule is only applied if selected tab indicator must be displayed."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"When the user taps a tab, the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"selectedTab"},{"type":"text","text":" binding is updated automatically, keeping the parent view in sync."}]},{"text":"Technical considerations","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Technical-considerations"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In order to improve the Developer eXperience the current "},{"code":"OUDSTabBar","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation lets users define their own tab items."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"OUDS applies only appearances and styles on elements to prevent users to define raw data to assign to the component before being rendered like a "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"picker"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Thus users will need to add their own accessiiblity label if badges are used or also apply "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"template"}]},{"type":"text","text":" rendering mode on images if needed."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Thus it will be also possible to use Liquid Glass new API with animations and items stacking."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You must use in your tab bar items images with "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"a size of 26 x 26"}]},{"type":"text","text":", otherwise rendering could be unaligned with Figma specifications"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Because the component cannot compute the ideal width of the selected tab indicator (for iOS before 26 and iPadOS before 18), ideal width based on the tab bar item content,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"this indicator is not displayed for iOS lower than 26 in landscape mode and iPadOS.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If your app uses several universes with nested views, containing their own navigation and tab bars, prefer "},{"code":"hideTabBar()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" from "},{"code":"View","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to hide the tab bar"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"("},{"code":"TabView","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and overlay items) with Liquid Glass is disabled or not available, or also "},{"code":"tabBar(isHidden:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"text":"Code samples","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Code-samples"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Use the OUDS tab bar to wrap tab bar items and associated views","    \/\/ Item tagged 0 will be selected first, 3 tabs are embedded.","    \/\/ Image with size of 26 x 26","    @State private var selectedTab = 0","","    OUDSTabBar(selectedTab: $selectedTab, count: 3) {","","        \/\/ Add the views with the SwiftUI tab item and labels","        \/\/ No need to define colors, everything is done inside OUDSTabBar","        SomeView()","            .tabItem {","                Label(\"Label 1\", image: \"image_1\")","            }","            .tag(0) \/\/ Must match the selectedTab binding value","        OtherView()","            .tabItem {","                Label {","                    Text(\"Label 2\")","                } icon: {","                    Image(decorative: \"image_2\")","                        .renderingMode(.template) \/\/ Mandatory to apply color on selected item","                }","             }","            .tag(1) \/\/ Must be used for the selectedTab binding","        LastView()","            .tabItem {","                Label(\"Label 3\", image: \"image_3\")","            }","            .tag(2) \/\/ Must be used for the selectedTab binding","    }"]},{"text":"Design documentation","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Design-documentation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-ios-tab-bar"}]},{"text":"Themes rendering","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Themes-rendering"},{"text":"Liquid Glass","level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Liquid-Glass"},{"text":"Orange","level":4,"type":"heading","anchor":"Orange"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_Orange_light"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_Orange_dark"}]},{"text":"Orange Compact","level":4,"type":"heading","anchor":"Orange-Compact"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_OrangeCompact_light"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_OrangeCompact_dark"}]},{"text":"Sosh","level":4,"type":"heading","anchor":"Sosh"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_Sosh_light"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_Sosh_dark"}]},{"text":"Wireframe","level":4,"type":"heading","anchor":"Wireframe"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_Wireframe_light"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_Wireframe_dark"}]},{"text":"Without Liquid Glass","level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Without-Liquid-Glass"},{"text":"Orange","level":4,"type":"heading","anchor":"Orange"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tabBar_Orange_light"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tabBar_Orange_dark"}]},{"text":"Orange Compact","level":4,"type":"heading","anchor":"Orange-Compact"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tabBar_OrangeCompact_light"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tabBar_OrangeCompact_dark"}]},{"text":"Sosh","level":4,"type":"heading","anchor":"Sosh"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tabBar_Sosh_light"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tabBar_Sosh_dark"}]},{"text":"Wireframe","level":4,"type":"heading","anchor":"Wireframe"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tabBar_Wireframe_light"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tabBar_Wireframe_dark"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1.0.0 (Figma component design version)"}]}],"type":"aside","name":"Version","style":"note"},{"name":"Since","style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1.0.0"}]}],"type":"aside"}]}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTabBar","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"text":"The Tab bar is a system navigation component with a position which can vary depending to the OS.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The tab bar can be found at the bottom of the screen for iOS. It can vary for iPadOS.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It allows users to switch between the sections of an app.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Each tab can be represented by a label, optionally paired with an icon, and maintains persistent visibility across top-level destinations.","type":"text"}],"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTabBar\/init(content:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTabBar\/init(selectedTab:count:content:)"],"generated":true,"title":"Initializers","anchor":"Initializers"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTabBar\/body"],"generated":true,"title":"Instance Properties","anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTabBar\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTabBar\/View-Implementations"],"generated":true,"title":"Default Implementations","anchor":"Default-Implementations"}],"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To"}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"struct","platforms":[{"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"introducedAt":"15.0","name":"iOS","deprecated":false},{"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"introducedAt":"13.0","name":"macOS","deprecated":false},{"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"introducedAt":"1.0","name":"visionOS","deprecated":false}],"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSTabBar","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSTabBar","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Structure","title":"OUDSTabBar","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents10OUDSTabBarV"},"references":{"component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_Wireframe_dark":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_Wireframe_dark.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image","alt":"A  tab bar component in dark mode with Liquid Glass effect and Wireframe theme","identifier":"component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_Wireframe_dark"},"component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_OrangeCompact_light":{"identifier":"component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_OrangeCompact_light","type":"image","alt":"A  tab bar component in light mode with Liquid Glass effect and Orange Compact theme","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_OrangeCompact_light.png","traits":["1x","light"]}]},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSTabBar/body":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"body"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"some"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"View","preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI4ViewP"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudstabbar\/body","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Uses a native SwiftUI "},{"code":"TabView","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" populated with the given content where "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"tab item"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" elements are defined."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Rendering wil change depending to OS version, with a top divider and a selected tab indicator for legacy layouts."}],"type":"topic","title":"body","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTabBar\/body"},"component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_Sosh_dark":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_Sosh_dark.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image","alt":"A  tab bar component in dark mode with Liquid Glass effect and Sosh theme","identifier":"component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_Sosh_dark"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents":{"images":[{"identifier":"ic_folder_categories.png","type":"icon"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The catalog of all components provided by OUDS. It contains also "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"View"},{"type":"text","text":" extensions and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewModifiers"},{"type":"text","text":" to apply tokens and styles on components and higher-level views."}],"title":"Components","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"},"component_tabBar_Orange_dark":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/component_tabBar_Orange_dark.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image","alt":"A tab bar component in dark mode without Liquid Glass effect and Orange theme","identifier":"component_tabBar_Orange_dark"},"https://r.orange.fr/r/S-ouds-doc-ios-tab-bar":{"type":"link","title":"unified-design-system.orange.com","url":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-ios-tab-bar","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unified-design-system.orange.com"}],"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-ios-tab-bar"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSTabBar/init(selectedTab:count:content:)":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"init"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"selectedTab"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI7BindingV","text":"Binding"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"},{"kind":"text","text":">, "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"count"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5UInt8V","text":"UInt8"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"content"},{"kind":"text","text":": () -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Content"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Defines the tab bar component with given tab bar items and a two-way binding to the selected tab index."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Number of tabs and selected tab are needed to compute the selected tab indicator for iOS lower than 26."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If you target iOS 26+ or other platform, prefer instead "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTabBar(content:)"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTabBar\/init(selectedTab:count:content:)","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudstabbar\/init(selectedtab:count:content:)","title":"init(selectedTab:count:content:)"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSBadge":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Badge is a UI element that emphasizes system notifications, status, or the categorization of an information, throughout colour only."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Badge is rendered as a coloured shape, without icon, text or number; and its chosen size remains unchanged regardless of the changes of the interface size."}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsbadge","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSBadge"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBadge","kind":"symbol","title":"OUDSBadge","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSBadge"}]},"component_tabBar_OrangeCompact_light":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/component_tabBar_OrangeCompact_light.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image","alt":"A  tab bar component in light mode without Liquid Glass effect and Orange Compact theme","identifier":"component_tabBar_OrangeCompact_light"},"component_tabBar_Wireframe_dark":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/component_tabBar_Wireframe_dark.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image","alt":"A  tab bar component in dark mode without Liquid Glass effect and Wireframe theme","identifier":"component_tabBar_Wireframe_dark"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSTabBar":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSTabBar"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSTabBar"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudstabbar","title":"OUDSTabBar","type":"topic","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Tab bar is a system navigation component with a position which can vary depending to the OS."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The tab bar can be found at the bottom of the screen for iOS. It can vary for iPadOS."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It allows users to switch between the sections of an app."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Each tab can be represented by a label, optionally paired with an icon, and maintains persistent visibility across top-level destinations."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTabBar"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSTabBar/init(content:)":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"init"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"content"},{"kind":"text","text":": () -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Content"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudstabbar\/init(content:)","title":"init(content:)","type":"topic","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Defines the tab bar component with given tab bar items."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If you target iOS lower than 26, prefer instead "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTabBar(selectedTab:count:content:)"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTabBar\/init(content:)"},"component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_Orange_light":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_Orange_light.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image","alt":"A tab bar component in light mode with Liquid Glass effect and Orange theme","identifier":"component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_Orange_light"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/Navigations":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Some components can be used for "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"navigation"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"role":"article","type":"topic","kind":"article","title":"Navigations","images":[{"identifier":"ic_folder_categories.png","type":"icon"},{"identifier":"ic_folder_categories.png","type":"card"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Navigations","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/navigations"},"component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_Orange_dark":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_Orange_dark.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image","alt":"A tab bar component in dark mode with Liquid Glass effect and Orange theme","identifier":"component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_Orange_dark"},"doc://OUDSComponents/7SwiftUI4ViewP":{"type":"unresolvable","title":"SwiftUICore.View","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"},"component_tabBar_OrangeCompact_dark":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/component_tabBar_OrangeCompact_dark.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image","alt":"A  tab bar component in dark mode without Liquid Glass effect and Orange Compact theme","identifier":"component_tabBar_OrangeCompact_dark"},"component_tabBar_Sosh_dark":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/component_tabBar_Sosh_dark.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image","alt":"A  tab bar component in dark mode without Liquid Glass effect and Sosh theme","identifier":"component_tabBar_Sosh_dark"},"doc://OUDSComponents/s8SendableP":{"type":"unresolvable","title":"Swift.Sendable","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP"},"ic_folder_categories.png":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/ic_folder_categories.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image","alt":null,"identifier":"ic_folder_categories.png"},"component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_Wireframe_light":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_Wireframe_light.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image","alt":"A  tab bar component in light mode with Liquid Glass effect and Wireframe theme","identifier":"component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_Wireframe_light"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSTabBar/View-Implementations":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudstabbar\/view-implementations","title":"View Implementations","type":"topic","role":"collectionGroup","abstract":[],"kind":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTabBar\/View-Implementations"},"component_tabBar_Wireframe_light":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/component_tabBar_Wireframe_light.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image","alt":"A  tab bar component in light mode without Liquid Glass effect and Wireframe theme","identifier":"component_tabBar_Wireframe_light"},"component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_Sosh_light":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_Sosh_light.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image","alt":"A  tab bar component in light mode with Liquid Glass effect and Sosh theme","identifier":"component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_Sosh_light"},"component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_OrangeCompact_dark":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_OrangeCompact_dark.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image","alt":"A  tab bar component in dark mode with Liquid Glass effect and Orange Compact theme","identifier":"component_tabBar_LiquidGlass_OrangeCompact_dark"},"component_tabBar_Orange_light":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/component_tabBar_Orange_light.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image","alt":"A tab bar component in light mode without Liquid Glass effect and Orange theme","identifier":"component_tabBar_Orange_light"},"doc://OUDSComponents/s16SendableMetatypeP":{"type":"unresolvable","title":"Swift.SendableMetatype","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP"},"component_tabBar_Sosh_light":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/component_tabBar_Sosh_light.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image","alt":"A  tab bar component in light mode without Liquid Glass effect and Sosh theme","identifier":"component_tabBar_Sosh_light"}}}